<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6080159>
    dc:description "FIG. 2. — Rinacapritermes abundans Amina & Rajmohana,n. gen., n. sp.: A, soldier body dorsal view; B, soldier head dorsal view; C, soldier head profile; D, soldier’s labrum; E, soldier’s Postmentum; F, worker left and right mandible. Scale bars: A, 0.5 mm; B, F, 0.3 mm; C, 0.2 mm; D, E, 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6080159/files/figure.png" ;
